26#include <sys/cdefs.h>
27__KERNEL_RCSID(0, "$NetBSD: nouveau_nvkm_engine_gr_gt215.c,v 1.2 2018/08/27 04:58:32 riastradh Exp $");
28
29#include "nv50.h"
30
31static const struct nvkm_gr_func
32gt215_gr = {
33 .init = nv50_gr_init,
34 .intr = nv50_gr_intr,
35 .chan_new = nv50_gr_chan_new,
36 .tlb_flush = g84_gr_tlb_flush,
37 .units = nv50_gr_units,
38 .sclass = {
39 { -1, -1, 0x0030, &nv50_gr_object },
40 { -1, -1, 0x502d, &nv50_gr_object },
41 { -1, -1, 0x5039, &nv50_gr_object },
42 { -1, -1, 0x50c0, &nv50_gr_object },
43 { -1, -1, 0x8597, &nv50_gr_object },
44 { -1, -1, 0x85c0, &nv50_gr_object },
45 {}
46 }
47};
48
49int
50gt215_gr_new(struct nvkm_device *device, int index, struct nvkm_gr **pgr)
51{
52 return nv50_gr_new_(&gt215_gr, device, index, pgr);
53}
